title: Stelpe Parish
text: Stelpe Parish () is an administrative unit of <a href="Bauska%20Municipality">Bauska Municipality</a> in the <a href="Semigallia">Semigallia</a> region of <a href="Latvia">Latvia</a>. Prior to 2009, it was part of the former <a href="Bauska%20District">Bauska District</a>.
